{"tid":2013100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"基本Twitter戰線教學上線","createTime":"2020-05-12T05:52:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T13:58:37.000Z","uid":167506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"898cefc77b1b0a2e6149b566fe93ee0551c7e071","tid":2013100,"uid":167506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T05:52:14.000Z","msg":"唔想再見到直播淨係可以好嬲好嬲？<br />\n<br />\n好想煲大粒核彈？<br />\n<br />\n好想外國出手幫我地？<br />\n<br />\n唔知twitter戰線要從何入手？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先我地要follow唔同嘅page<br />\n<br />\n然後每日花五分鐘開twitter出嚟retweet&amp;like<br />\n<br />\n咁就完成任務架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只要follow哂啲page，以後一開twitter就可以啪啪啪咁like同retweet哂所有post喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔洗再辛苦手足整合幾廿個post<br />\n<br />\n唔洗再等bot餵到埋口<br />\n<br />\n想煲大邊粒核彈就煲大邊粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁低成本高回報嘅野，唔係唔做呀？<br />\n<br />\n最後整合左幾個twitter page比大家follow<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，歡迎各位手足喺樓下補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n周庭<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/chowtingagnes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchowtingagnes&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmBnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=9b114031\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/chowtingagnes</a><br />\n<br />\nGphone<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/joshuawongcf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjoshuawongcf&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmBnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=a3b22b41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/joshuawongcf</a><br />\n<br />\n毛EE<br />\n<a