br />\n入bot 拎任務24小時更新：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmBnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=f1c7d9d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<br />\n另有手足會係佢Twitter Account 每日更新任務:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/TweetingforHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTweetingforHK&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmBnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=acb4419e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/TweetingforHK</a><br />\n<br />\n或者download 香城online 個app 都有Twitter 任務做<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/HKOnlinePortal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FHKOnlinePortal&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmBnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=9c7cbbd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/HKOnlinePortal</a><br />\n<br />\nLike retweet reply<br />\nTask2係國際戰線，唔好淨係推Task 1,Task2都好重要。<br />\n*如果見到想用嘅圖已經有手足用咗請搵第二張圖<br />\n*如果見到已經有好多圖就唔好再放圖，只留文字（短短地都得）<br />\n*唔好只係扔低張圖咩字都唔打<br />\n*唔知留咩好就like 手足留言或者啲對我哋有利嘅留言<br />\n<br />\n將Twitter 變成日常，每人每日做少少。<br />\n每人嘅一小步加埋就係一大步。<br />\n我哋唔知做咩先有用，所以咩都試下咩都做下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3aa1f622142ff557f74be02ca75a25dd642afd5","tid":2013100,"uid":34594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:31:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"45a84736be3ea755f29e8cef9eefbc4301f87d2f","tid":2013100,"uid":177679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:26:54.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推twitter重要啊！"},{"pid":"3437164401529ed68461547101ad3d88a5ddfcb0","tid":2013100,"uid":203685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T13:58:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20214f6f7f5d719cf0104b30df067d5ff891a8b8","tid":2013100,"uid":203685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T13:58:37.000Z","msg":"推"}]}